text: Very good morning! :slightly_smiling_face:. I'am aware of many cheap hotels in Pune. here are some for you!
Does the 4th hotel has parking facility?
I am sorry! :disappointed: the 4th hotel doesn't provide parking facility. You can try the other hotels. :slightly_smiling_face:
Sure then I would like to check the 2nd image.:disappointed:
Please have a look at the parking area :slightly_smiling_face: from the 2nd image.
This looks very unpleasant and crowded :pensive:. Can you show some other hotels with good parking area.
Oh! please don't be sad. I have some more better options for you. :slightly_smiling_face:
This seems better:slightly_smiling_face:. Can you tell the price of the rooms?
The 1st one if for 1000/- Rs per night, 2nd is for 950/- Rs, 3rd one is for 800/- per night and last one is 650/- only. :slightly_smiling_face:
The 1st one looks pretty nice:smiley:. can you show the images from all the orientation of the 1st image?
Hey!. I don't have the images form different orientations of the same room but I do have some other rooms of the same price. :blush:
This doesn't seem as cosy and homey as the previous image.:face_with_raised_eyebrow: Can you tell the other amenities that the hotel offer?
hey! when you stay here you get to experience free wifi, the breakfast is complementary. :wink:
This seems nice:grin:. Can you show the sitting area where they serve the meals?
They serve their meals here in the dining area. :slightly_smiling_face:
Alright it looks clean and comfortable:relieved:.
Yups! it is. Do you want any other information? :relaxed:
No, thanks for the help:slightly_smiling_face:
Do you want to book a room in this hotel? :face_with_raised_eyebrow:
Not at this moment but I might book later.:no_mouth:
Okay! Not a problem. Have a nice day!! :slightly_smiling_face:
